hopobject.body: Very funny pictures buff bake protein cookie nutrition facts It's a girl for Jessica Alba! The actress and husband Cash Warren welcomed daughter Haven Garner Warren to their brood on Aug. 13. ‘She was born on Saturday, weighed 7 lbs. and was 19 inches long. Healthy and happy!’ Alba, 30, wrote on her official Facebook page. ‘Big sister Honor couldn't be more excited about the new addition to our family.’ This is the second child for the couple, who met while filming ‘Fantastic Four’ and wed in 2008.
